          %.*
          %.*fetched libbar/0.0.1%
          unpacked libbar/0.0.1
          configured libbar/0.0.1
          EOE

        $* '?sys:libbaz/0.0.1' 2>>~%EOE%;
          disfigured libbar/0.0.1
          disfigured libbaz/0.0.1
          disfigured libfox/0.0.1
          purged libfox/0.0.1
          purged libbaz/0.0.1
